WEBVTT

00:00.211 --> 00:04.041
What if all the travelers could discuss, invite, exchange views...

00:04.131 --> 00:06.739
...and finalize the trip on one common platform?

00:07.304 --> 00:09.125
Now, JustOrbit is here!

00:09.719 --> 00:11.321
Do everything under one roof.

00:11.658 --> 00:13.453
Find the destinations you wish to visit.

00:13.782 --> 00:15.396
Find the perfect destination.

00:15.882 --> 00:18.401
Add and remove cities to visit with just a click.

00:18.817 --> 00:21.598
Find and add attractions and activities to your itinerary.

00:21.892 --> 00:24.979
Include all the local activities which you would like to explore.

00:25.359 --> 00:29.349
Save the trip and easily share all the details with whoever you want.

00:29.815 --> 00:32.973
The benefits of planning your trip with JustOrbit include:...

00:33.406 --> 00:36.817
...all invited members receive an email with all the trip details.

00:37.329 --> 00:39.841
All trip plans come with an authentication code.

00:40.100 --> 00:42.915
Simply click, enter the code and start discussing.

00:44.431 --> 00:48.601
Once a member is satisfied with the plans, they can request trip finalization,...

00:48.939 --> 00:51.353
...followed by the creator, putting a freeze on the trip.

00:51.926 --> 00:54.366
The next step is booking hotels and attractions.

00:57.628 --> 01:01.413
Plus, there is a variety of suggested tour packages based on your plans...

01:01.568 --> 01:02.835
...to make it even easier.

01:04.012 --> 01:06.386
Bookings done, now it's time to travel.

01:06.946 --> 01:09.645
Travel planning is easy with JustOrbit.com.

